	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're in middle school, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> These are the years when everything seems to change at once — your body, your friends, your phone, the way people look at you. You might feel left out, compared, picked on, or just weird, like you don't fit anywhere. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a Bible you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on any phone — and it shows you something steady underneath all the change: you have a Father in heaven who already knows you completely and loves you completely. Whether you searched "Bible verses for middle schoolers," "verses when you feel left out," or "Bible verses about anxiety," it all comes back to one thing — you are His beloved child, and you don't have to earn that.`}
