	offersBlocks={[
		{ heading: `A place you already belong`, bodyHtml: `You don't have to win your way in. Through Jesus, your Father gives you <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/john/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">the right to be His child</a> — a belonging no group chat can give or take away.` },
		{ heading: `A Father who sees the real you`, bodyHtml: `While everyone judges by looks, <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/1-samuel/16" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father looks at your heart</a>. He knows the you behind the screen and the smile — and He loves that you.` },
		{ heading: `Calm when you're anxious`, bodyHtml: `When worry tightens your chest, your Father says <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/41" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">"do not fear, I am with you."</a> He holds you up when middle school feels like too much.` },
