		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a stranger`, bodyHtml: `Lots of Bibles can feel distant. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on — so the God you read feels like the steady, loving Dad you can actually talk to.` },
		{ heading: `You can listen, not just read`, bodyHtml: `Every chapter is free to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">read online with audio</a>. Pop in headphones on the bus or before bed and let your Father's words be the loudest voice in your day — louder than the comparison and the noise online.` },
